OL,7,FThree out of four primary school
OL,8,Fteachers think children's physical
OL,9,Factivity is declining, research
OL,10,Fsuggests.
OL,12,FHalf of 500 teachers surveyed said
OL,13,Fthey believe fewer than one in two
OL,14,Fchildren in their class could run a
OL,15,Fmile.
