OL,3,CMajority of primary teachers fear
OL,4,Cpupils' physical activity declining `
OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,FThe Daily Mile, a charity which
OL,8,Fencourages school children to run the
OL,9,Fequivalent of a mile every day, said
OL,10,Fits study found most primary school
OL,11,Fteachers do not think pupils in their
OL,12,Fclass are active enough.
OL,14,FMost respondents said children
OL,15,Factively avoid being physically active
OL,16,Fduring break times, which they believe
OL,17,Fis having a direct impact on
OL,18,Fyoungsters' health and development.
