OL,7,FElaine Wyllie, a former headteacher of
OL,8,FSt Ninians Primary School in Stirling
OL,9,Fand founder of the Daily Mile, said:
OL,10,F"Children's physical fitness is
OL,11,Fparamount to both health and academic
OL,12,Foutcomes.
OL,14,F"The proven success of the Daily Mile
OL,15,Fmakes it clear that building healthy
OL,16,Fhabits for life can be affordable,
OL,17,Finclusive and simple."
